  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p>1. This Competition is open to people aged 18 or over.</p>
<p>2. Employees or agencies of Inghams or their family members, or anyone else connected with the Prize Draw may not enter the Prize Draw.</p>
<p>3. Entrants into the Competition shall be deemed to have accepted these Terms and Conditions.</p>
<p>4. To enter the Competition you must like the <a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.facebook.com/inghams/" target="_blank">Inghams Facebook page</a> and also share either the Friday or the Tuesday post of the corresponding week, within the below time frames:</p>
<p>- Competition post 1 - Scheduled at 12:30pm on 01/09/2017</p>
<p>- Competition post 2 - Scheduled at 12:30pm on 05/09/2017</p>
<p>- Competition post 3 - Scheduled at 12:30pm on 08/09/2017</p>
<p>- Competition post 4 - Scheduled at 12:30pm on 12/09/2017</p>
<p>5. Only one entry per person per Competition week. Entries on behalf of another person will not be accepted and joint submissions are not allowed.</p>
<p>6. Inghams accepts no responsibility for entries that are lost, delayed, misdirected or incomplete.</p>
<p>7. <span class="TextRun SCXW111546033"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW111546033">One</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW111546033"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW111546033"> winner will be chosen a random draw of entries, received in accordance with these Terms and Conditions. The draw will be chosen at random by Inghams. The draw will take place on the Friday </span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW111546033"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW111546033">15</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW111546033"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW111546033" data-fontsize="11">th</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW111546033"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW111546033"> September 2017</span></span>.</p>
<p>8. Inghams accepts no responsibility for any costs associated with the prize and not specifically included in the prize.</p>
<p>9. The winner of each week will be notified by Facebook Message at the end of the corresponding Competition week. If a winner does not respond to Inghams within 14 days of being notified by Inghams, then the winner's prize will be forfeited and Inghams shall be entitled to select another winner in accordance with the process described above (and that winner will have to respond to notification of their win within 14 days or else they will also forfeit their prize). If a winner rejects their prize or the entry is invalid or in breach of these Terms and Conditions, the winner's prize will be forfeited and Inghams shall be entitled to select another winner. The winner will be announced on the Inghams Facebook page at the end of the corresponding Competition week.</p>
<p>10. <span class="TextRun SCXW213203945"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW213203945">The ski glove prize</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW213203945"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW213203945"> include</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW213203945"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW213203945">s</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW213203945"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW213203945"> an option between the Mount Babel, Mount Bowlen, Mount Fay and Mount </span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW213203945"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW213203945">Little</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW213203945"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW213203945"> styles</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW213203945"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW213203945"> of 10 Peak</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW213203945"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW213203945"> </span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW213203945"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW213203945">Gloves </span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW213203945"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW213203945">only.</span></span></p>
<p>11. The winner will be contacted via Facebook Messenger and requested to supply the following information:</p>
<p>- The type of ski gloves they would like to receive from the options given in point 10</p>
<p>- The size of glove they wish for each pair of gloves (a measurement link will be provided to each winner)</p>
<p>- The address where the winner would like the prizes to be sent to.</p>
<p>12. <span class="TextRun SCXW56429687"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW56429687">The</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW56429687"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW56429687"> prize</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW56429687"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW56429687"> will be deli</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW56429687"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW56429687">vered to the Competition winner</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW56429687"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW56429687"> via Inghams after </span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW56429687"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW56429687">the competition has</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW56429687"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW56429687"> finished.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW56429687" data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}"> </span></p>
<p>13. The prize is non-exchangeable, non-transferable, and is not redeemable for cash or other prizes.</p>
<p>14. Inghams shall use and take care of any personal information you supply to it as described in its privacy policy, and in accordance with data protection legislation.</p>
<p>15. Inghams accepts no responsibility for any damage, loss, liabilities, injury or disappointment incurred or suffered by you as a result of entering the Competition or accepting the prize. Inghams further disclaims liability for any injury or damage to your or any other person's computer relating to or resulting from participation in or downloading any materials in connection with the Competition.</p>
<p>16. Inghams reserves the right at any time and from time to time to modify or discontinue, temporarily or permanently, this Competition with or without prior notice due to reasons outside its control (including, without limitation, in the case of anticipated, suspected or actual fraud). The decision of Inghams in all matters under its control is final and binding and no correspondence will be entered into.</p>
<p>17. Inghams shall not be liable for any failure to comply with its obligations where the failure is caused by something outside its reasonable control. Such circumstances shall include, but not be limited to, weather conditions, fire, flood, hurricane, strike, industrial dispute, war, hostilities, political unrest, riots, civil commotion, inevitable accidents, supervening legislation or any other circumstances amounting to force majeure.</p>
<p>18. The Competition will be governed by English law and entrants to the Competition submit to the exclusive jurisdiction of the English courts.</p>
<p>19. Promoter: Inghams Holidays, Mountain House, Station Road, Surrey, GU7 1EX.</p>
</div>
